&lt;P&gt;Well, I've seen a barbarian block the door to the bank in Kelethin. Did you know you can go along the outside of the bank and switch to 3rd person view and move the view around so you can see the banker through the window, and click on him and do your banking while you are outside the bank still? This works from quite a ways away from the banker, actually. I've used this method a lot. Especially when I tried out a barbarian and came to visit my wife the elf. A barbarian can't get through that door unless they do some sorta crab walking sideways while crouched down. Something like that. So much easier to just use the third person view and select the banker through the window.&lt;/P&gt;</description>
